D-FINE-cpp is a C++/TensorRT inference port of D-FINE
(https://github.com/Peterande/D-FINE), which is licensed under Apache-2.0.

Bundled / vendored third-party components:
  - third_party/stb (stb_image) — public domain / MIT
  - nlohmann/json — MIT (fetched at build time)

This software links against NVIDIA TensorRT and NVIDIA CUDA, which are
proprietary NVIDIA SDKs. They are not distributed with this repository;
the user must install them separately.
